Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As discussed, we've decided to perform operation "Golden Apple".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Bianca...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be in charge of this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, the goal of this mission is to capture the target alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can use it for our research material.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get information as to her whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for the good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:59.48,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The constellations that decorate the summer night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:05.19,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The diamonds start to twinkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:11.12,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting go into the time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:17.50,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to warm the body, tired from swimming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:29.81,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended not to notice the smile that hides the loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:36.82,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's an endless dream (Keep on going)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:42.09,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight and shine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:48.77,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in your true self (It's up to you)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:54.10,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:02:02.34,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Look only at the irreplaceable future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:14.11,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,322)}The Golden Delmo Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, work's been getting done quite satisfactorily. Hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have something to tell everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we came a long way to the south...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To show my appreciation for all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made plans to stay one night at a resort hotel on Peroronka Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Papa. Call me President!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we afford it, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, our company has been doing better recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should return something to my employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a reservation under the name of the K2 Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We reserved the rooms for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is super cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could sure live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika, let's go to the pool! The pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Can you wait a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't use a lot of this, I'll be very sorry later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me he had to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. He is probably doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean, Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you bring the same drink for this lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm the one who caused you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have just arrived at this hotel today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's no way I could've overlooked such a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're quite the charmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have your name? If you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Pierre Valimore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aika. Aika Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an exotic name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be related to some noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been staying here long, Mr. Valimore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Pierre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been here long, Pierre?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm here for vacation, but I was getting bored recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a beautiful woman like you showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This certainly is good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a charmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to do it, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we going through so much trouble to capture one woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be satisfied by just physically capturing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to completely humiliate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? You're in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Aika is a rather imprudent person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps she's feeling a bit liberated, here on the southern island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean running off with such a cheap, flashy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should find a nice guy too, Rion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little lost. Which way is the elevator?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go over there, and make a left...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:10:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? We're also from Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're going to the beach now. Do you want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go and let's do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! One more round. Give me the chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We captured two of the targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are also holding the last target.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We're about to head back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my companions aren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might be in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not usually such an impulsive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is wrong with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the southern ocean has a strange effect on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does, doesn't it? It must.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel really strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can happen to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre, you are really a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know about my true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good, Pierre... Having your way with a drunk woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika Sumeragi, I've been waiting for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will share a secret with you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has worked out as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you'll watch your friends struggle in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll die! They'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you want to save them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm awake now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drug isn't working on her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Bianca, the purpose of this mission is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already kissed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all Hargen's people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to get revenge for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Hargen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would take a long time to explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but let's just say, they're the villains!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Hargen's people are all over this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find the president first, and then get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that guy also working for them, Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please don't bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy wasn't a guy, he's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really fooled by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen such a gorgeous guy as me, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Valerie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be satisfied, just shooting you dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Bianca. Request a mobile unit air strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger! We will rush to get over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's Aika doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be an armored car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that by looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, why did it suddenly appear out of nowhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I your target?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:18:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss Bianca.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she have to take my job?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this water?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another one. Get in quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't beat them this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an easy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Bianca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this turned out to be a terrible vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Hargen's people could attack us at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this Hargen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy named Hargen planned to rule the earth using the power of Raggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Raggu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Raggu?... Well, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume Aika and her companions already escaped from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, she wasn't so easy to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take the next action immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation "Silver Wild Grapevine" is already prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:45.35,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,So dance with me tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:49.33,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not above being cool for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:53.50,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, tell me what you want, what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:57.60,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,In the hardest time, you still look so good to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:02.00,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can ease your mind, ease your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:05.91,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have your fears just like every man
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.91,0:23:09.74,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Cannot be sure of yourself all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.48,0:23:14.72,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Just close your eyes, I'll turn the music on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:18.71,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're gonna do what you got to do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:26.85,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,So dance with me tonight, 'cause I make you feel all right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:30.76,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Who fell in love at sight? I don't want to make a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:34.90,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Just dance with me tonight, if you wanna hold me tight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:38.07,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say maybe, come to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:43.37,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,So dance with me tonight, 'cause I make you feel all right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:47.42,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Who fell in love at sight? I don't want to make a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:51.49,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Just dance with me tonight, if you wanna hold me tight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.55,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say maybe, come to me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.07,0:24:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big company hires the K2 Corporation for an investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we head north.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.41,0:24:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arriving at their installation,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we meet a beautiful young girl, an ace fighter pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To test my compatibility with the Probe-jet,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.55,0:24:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she requests that I take a pre-flight exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.66,0:24:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this girl intend to do to Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.53,0:24:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is totally suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.76,0:24:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After thoroughly examining me, the Delmos reveal themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.17,0:24:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While escaping with my data,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.50,0:24:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the beautiful young Delmo girl launches a cunning attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.57,0:24:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika, next trial:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.46,0:25:00.46,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,342)}Delmo Operation: "White Silver"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.46,0:24:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delmo Operation: "White Silver"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.98,0:24:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat from this fierce battle with the beautiful Delmo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.55,0:24:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could even melt snow.
